      "index": "z00011",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "• both under orderR.Use(authMW) — token\n  mandatory (catalog was public).\n• created_by rule (handler:88-92):\n  role==customer → blanked → NULL;\n  staff JWT → stores staff subject.\n• guest ownership BY TABLE not id:\n  callerID = claims.TableID;\n  GetOrder enforces o.TableID==callerID\n  (service:116-120).\n• ⚠ online (table NULL) → 403 for\n  customer role (Bug 3).",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• both under orderR.Use(authMW) — token\n  mandatory (catalog was public).\n• created_by rule (handler:88-92):\n  role==customer → blanked → NULL;\n  staff JWT → stores staff subject.\n• guest ownership BY TABLE not id:\n  callerID = claims.TableID;\n  GetOrder enforces o.TableID==callerID\n  (service:116-120).\n• ⚠ online (table NULL) → 403 for\n  customer role (Bug 3).",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
