      "frameId": null,
      "text": "radio (page.tsx:24-29,184-194) → cart.setPaymentMethod → clearCart wipes it.\nNOT in POST body · no orders.payment_method column (DB_SCHEMA:138).\nVNPay/MoMo/ZaloPay do nothing. Fix: FE drop non-cash / disable.",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "radio (page.tsx:24-29,184-194) → cart.setPaymentMethod → clearCart wipes it.\nNOT in POST body · no orders.payment_method column (DB_SCHEMA:138).\nVNPay/MoMo/ZaloPay do nothing. Fix: FE drop non-cash / disable.",
