      "index": "z00024",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "TableConfirmModal calls setActiveOrderId(id) after create → /tracking knows the order immediately.\n/checkout does NOT — clearCart() resets activeOrderId to null (cart.ts:89). Guest must tap \"Theo dõi bàn\"\non /order/<id> to set the pointer. Until then /tracking shows the empty state.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "TableConfirmModal calls setActiveOrderId(id) after create → /tracking knows the order immediately.\n/checkout does NOT — clearCart() resets activeOrderId to null (cart.ts:89). Guest must tap \"Theo dõi bàn\"\non /order/<id> to set the pointer. Until then /tracking shows the empty state.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
