      "text": "tap radio → RHF field → cart.setPaymentMethod('vnpay')  ✗ NOT in POST body  ✗ no orders column\n→ clearCart() wipes it. Lifecycle: selected → briefly stored → never sent → erased. Cosmetic today.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
